Unlimited food only @725 /-
Unlimited food, beer,wine,sangria 1059 /- 
Unlimited food, beer and imfl @1599 /-
(Taxes as applicable)

Live music by Austin 

The perfect Sunday awaits you at cafe1730.Meet up with family and friends in a relaxed ambiance, enjoying the most delicious brunch dishes and best wines in town.

  
The feast opens with a spectacular brunch of fresh salads, home made pastries and the best local fishes and cheeses. But there is more, The al a carte brunch menu offers a definite selection of seasonally inspired brunch dishbes. The Sunday is completed with the delightful dessert table full of treats no one should miss the Pure indulgence.
